Object.Pattern:
// Get whole region as subattr
  (?'ImageRegion'
    \A000-00-0000\z
  )
| // Find Month and Day as subattr
  \A\W{0,2}?
  (?'Nine'
      (JAN|FEB|MAR|APR|MAY|JUN|JUL|AUG|SEP|OCT|NOV|DEC)[\W+][X#*]{2}[\W+]
  )
| // Get whole string (minus leading/trailing ws) when 2-4 pattern
  // K:\Common\Engineering\Sample Files\AtPac\CA - ContraCosta\Set014\Images\19929020669999.008
  \A\s*
  (?'LastSeven'
    \d\s?\d\s?-\s?\d\s?\d\s?\d\s?\d\s?\d
  )\s*\z
| // Get whole string (minus leading/trailing ws) if on a single line
  \A\s*
  (?'SingleLine'
    [^\r\n]+
  )\s*\z
| // Get up to first newline (not counting leading ws)
  \A\s*
  (?'MultiLine'
    [^\r\n]+
  )
